0305151aeca6cc9c.voiceContent: My father would have a mesmerized look on his face whenever we got to that part of the story.

0795012c9a0bf3be.voiceContent: Yes, that's right. The legend had it that adepti could drift upon beams of light, ride lightning, and leap into the sky to ascend to their abode.

08232334edd20332.voiceContent: I want to hear all that you have to say! It truly is fascinating.

13f636abbc1c1094.voiceContent: If you could manage to find the time to sit and enjoy an opera together or share a pot of tea... Taking a moment to slow down and enjoy the finer things in life is always beneficial to your body and soul.

17e6c39796d1738e.voiceContent: After traveling to so many places, I'm sure that you've learned many different customs. Would you mind sharing some with me?

1910b7a941537f30.voiceContent: I've also heard that the swords produced in Inazuma can cut through nearly anything... How do they forge such sharp swords?

1ccda0f15a9f8b7b.voiceContent: Its name contains the word yun, just like my own name... It looks like I have a special connection with this room.

1f0ae40476ac6e0b.voiceContent: Then I won't beat around the bush.

2202c717f4d59cec.voiceContent: If you skip a day, only you will know. But if you skip three days, the whole audience will know. A master never forgets the fundamentals of practicing.

283b5e6688660e45.voiceContent: Alright, I have some ideas. I think for the performance, I will sing a selection about you and your dealings with the adepti...

2c953278359d7cbf.voiceContent: It can be difficult to find a suitable place where my singing won't disturb anyone in Liyue Harbor, but here that is not a problem at all.

36e9029b61247831.voiceContent: #Yes, good night, {NICKNAME}! It is good to turn in early from time to time.

3b2566f49c605acc.voiceContent: Let's just hope that the weather will hold up with no rain or storms, and that you can go speedily about your way.

408f910b186b25aa.voiceContent: It has always been my dream to go and see such a place one day.

4746d308d454bc84.voiceContent: Hmm, would you look at that... the name of this room is the Feiyun Study Room.

4815ebc9b1c242fe.voiceContent: Let's take a stroll around here tonight, then. What do you say?

502b951ee7f6bc97.voiceContent: To be completely honest, I find great enjoyment in my hours of practice.

58536e9e0e7d5e83.voiceContent: Oh, that must be a very special material, then... It's no wonder that the people of Inazuma are reputedly confident in their craftsmanship.

5accc2cb19c5d197.voiceContent: It's just that you've traveled extensively... you have much experience for me to draw upon.

5d4023231b3a0647.voiceContent: When I was a child, my father often told me legends of the adepti. I remember that one legend in particular made mention of an adeptus's abode in Jueyun Karst.

691b75c68d78d979.voiceContent: I have a habit of going to an open space every morning to rehearse my voice.

69e6a4904a54a4b8.voiceContent: Alright, it's settled. I'll start practicing today... Actually, why not start right away â€” no time like the present! I must make sure this performance turns out perfect.

71e92f120e43412d.voiceContent: From their lofty dwelling, they gaze to and fro. Drifting over land and sea, they know not the world below.

722f561d28eedc94.voiceContent: Haha, is this humor of yours also something that you've acquired throughout your travels?

794d51e0de89a057.voiceContent: However, in my practice routine, I tend to go over my whole repertoire, both singing and reciting... I may suddenly be acting dreadfully mournful one moment, and then practicing a hysterical laugh the next... I fear such a kaleidoscope of outright emotion may scare you.

7bcfb25751e4ac6b.voiceContent: Thank you very much! That's most kind of you.

7ec5d07f3d8ba5d6.voiceContent: As for the costume, I was hoping you could give me some creative input.

8a16952caa9fd97b.voiceContent: I'll be sure to prepare some more questions for the next time we talk.

8c56f4fd690ce983.voiceContent: Yes. Why, that's a fundamental part of anyone's routine in my profession.

8d80e10f138ee7bd.voiceContent: *sigh* Alright, I can see it written on your face already, That sounds exhausting... As a matter of fact, I don't feel that way at all, quite the opposite, really.

99a4258f53719e97.voiceContent: For example, the swordplay of the Knights in Mondstadt, what's that like? Does it differ from that of the martial artists we see in Liyue?

9ada2ef99dd1b532.voiceContent: Haha, I'm kidding, of course. It is most definitely to my liking, though. Furnished with all the supplies one could possibly hope for in a study. I am truly grateful.

a1280dc035d53087.voiceContent: This street has a striking resemblance to those back in Liyue. It really feels just like being there.

b09bb491f71f260e.voiceContent: The night markets are always worth a visit though, perhaps we can save that for tomorrow.

b400b53bd08d63e0.voiceContent: Yes, now that you mention it... there is one thing I have been meaning to do.

c0d1c49309d9a20b.voiceContent: #Ah, you've arrived, {NICKNAME}. I couldn't help but notice how busy you are these days...

c0ecdef12a5b7ff9.voiceContent: I would even like to perform an opera there, letting adepti and people alike hear my voice echoing through the lands.

c57cc302d7c098b3.voiceContent: But though the story has been passed down all these years, no one has yet to ever see such an abode...

cdca405e59a52a22.voiceContent: Ahem... I mean... I know that your words are sincere, it's just that you answered so quickly, and I haven't even decided what opera to perform or what costume to prepare...

ce6e33272b56918e.voiceContent: To fully deliver the elegance of Liyue opera to the audience, we must strive for excellence, properly performing every subtlety in the story.

d5cf856dd487cb83.voiceContent: Yes, that would be perfect. I've been meaning to ask for your guidance on many things.

d6f9717f7f09c9bd.voiceContent: Ahem, to be completely honest... There are times I have considered giving up the opera and taking time to travel around faraway nations. But things are always busy in the troupe and I've just never found the right opportunity.

da3954e507a7b230.voiceContent: I must respect you if I wish to gain from your experience.

edff40b89a4611ec.voiceContent: A fighting style that flows like the wind? I wonder, are they capable of even manipulating the wind in combat?

f5e12995d58599ab.voiceContent: Great. Thank you for your kind understanding.

f78fefe921e9754e.voiceContent: I would much prefer to offer you a complete and fully prepared opera instead.

f7e89fd8eb288e20.voiceContent: I always love to take a stroll around the night market after a performance.

f8b9e3facc6b80f0.voiceContent: Haha, how kind. I do appreciate your courtesy.

f8d747bdc12c9316.voiceContent: Yes, you needn't worry. Everything here seems to be in good order, not to mention the delightful scenery. I think I will have no issue residing in such a pleasant place.

fa3714dc8496fde3.voiceContent: Good morning. Will you be departing for adventures in a distant land today?

fc0881425b8a3a99.voiceContent: Of course, I'll be sure to make our conversations worth your time as well. I will prepare an appropriate gift for you as thanks for answering my questions.

0e1e68cab3e4141b.voiceContent: They're coming. Just do what you'd normally do in this situation.

031caff29dce52d5.voiceContent: Kaedehara Kazuha is among the many outlanders who enjoy Liyue opera. Whether it's an orchestral section or a percussive piece, he always sits there and listens quietly. Talk about great manners!

068bb0cd9fc06ddb.voiceContent: Now that I think about it, the Yun-Han Opera Troupe has been under my leadership for quite some time now. Before taking it over, I only knew two things how to write opera and how to perform it on stage. I never gave any thought to how to run a troupe. Becoming the troupe's director gave me a crash course in this unfamiliar area and I've experienced all the highs and lows of working with people along the way... Only now do I understand that life mirrors opera, just as opera reflects life.

088364cb045de757.voiceContent: *sigh* Well, as you can probably imagine, I always have to be mindful of what I eat and make sure I stay in shape. It's a shame, because the temptation to indulge in all the tasty delicacies the city has to offer is just as strong to me as to anyone else...

139f36b20f290a97.voiceContent: I began my training in the art of the spear hoping to enhance my performance in stage combat. I stuck with it hoping to master the techniques of self-defense. Today, it looks like I have finally achieved both of these goals.

182f22c3bc8e31b1.voiceContent: As the saying goes Achievement in a field is the result of how hard you are willing to work at it, not how much you enjoy it.

19bd4d6e810c3792.voiceContent: Mmm! There's no better feeling than indulging in your favorite food... It's a shame that I can only afford to have a little bite.

1ea0445dab17e619.voiceContent: The Tianquan is a big spender and has made several very generous donations to our troupe. I can only return her generosity by delivering my best possible performance.

25294a6f02266e1c.voiceContent: I'm sorry... This meal isn't really agreeing with me.

2a8b2489a4b66092.voiceContent: I'd like to indulge in a nap after lunch. Oh? ...You're not tired?

3593cef6c6d91306.voiceContent: Many of the operas we've been performing recently are new ones that I wrote after assuming the directorship of the troupe. I suppose the fact that I can both write and sing my own material has contributed to my rising popularity in Liyue Harbor.

370dfcdf6b74fdee.voiceContent: The chirping of the songbirds at daybreak always puts me in the best of moods.

41fc6871c5b08d38.voiceContent: Oh, what a magnificent feast! Wait a second, I'll grab us some drinks to accompany the meal.

43938caf3cd7bffc.voiceContent: As the saying goes, you never truly know someone until you meet them in person, and at long last, I finally have the great honor of meeting you today. My name is Yun Jin, and I am humbled to be the director of the Yun-Han Opera Troupe. We have been performing at Heyu Tea House as of late, and we'd be honored to have you attend a performance sometime.

461ef45a4cfa1321.voiceContent: Oh, so today's your birthday? Well, I wouldn't know how to throw you a feast if I tried... so how about I sing you a song? For you alone, an audience of one. So... what song would you like to hear me sing? The choice is yours.

482e14a15277d6ce.voiceContent: The elders of the troupe are always harping on about rock 'n' roll being a bad influence. Needless to say, they never approve of me going to see Xinyan's shows. It's for your own good, they say. Hmph, all it's really about is their inability to accept anything new. Whatever, those old fogies can't tell me what to do. I'm going to keep rocking out at Xinyan's gigs, every week, and that's that.

49dbfc5b91f37b63.voiceContent: Hmm? My Vision? Hehe, I suppose the Lord of Geo must be a fan of the opera. Perhaps the old man was so delighted with my performance that he decided to grant me a Vision.

4cc5e3090f127828.voiceContent: At the start of my opera career, I have to say I did let the standing ovations from our audiences go to my head a little. It wasn't long before I developed a captious attitude... If I didn't like the script, or if the stage was too small, or if I thought there weren't enough people in the audience, I would refuse to perform. Looking back now, it was all terribly arrogant of me... my goodness. I shall never let myself become so vain again.

5b4d56c224a7a404.voiceContent: (Translated) How gently do the clouds and flowers sway, as dancing winds meander through the vales.

62457cc9f61f99b3.voiceContent: Hmm... Anything the troupe could use on our journey?

7079f99f8a896982.voiceContent: I'm sorry... This meal isn't really agreeing with me.

75c357a98931d9cb.voiceContent: Sometimes, I just feel like casting off my opera costume and going traveling overseas. You know, to explore the outside world. For now, I'll need to keep working hard at what I'm doing, so someday that dream can come true.

812b484f6bb3527b.voiceContent: (Translated) Fie! This cold shall be mine end!

84973ed5e2f0e492.voiceContent: Well you know, many of Liyue's legends are centered around stories of gods and the adepti, so most operas focus on the supernatural, too. A prime example would be The Divine Damsel of Devastation, which we have been performing recently. Long-time opera fans adore this sort of material, but in this age of humanity, I would rather like to tell stories about ordinary people. Yes, how grand it would be to sing about the hopes and dreams of ordinary people for all to hear. I've never shared these thoughts with anyone before... Thank you for listening so patiently. I'm fortunate to have a close friend like you.

8a060f5b47483f21.voiceContent: Let's get this show on the road!

91e1d4ba5288df8e.voiceContent: It looks like all my rigorous training is finally paying off.

92a3acf5f28b347b.voiceContent: My schooling started very early. In fact, my earliest memories are of my father teaching me to read. Despite my best efforts, my ability is not half of his. Enough to write operas, but compared to his level of erudition, I still have much to strive for.

954fbf7547c4eab8.voiceContent: I have long since known The Divine Damsel of Devastation inside out, back to front, but it was only very recently that I learned that the divine damsel in question is actually a real person. Life is full of strange twists sometimes! My only hope is that she can find true friendship and never be lonely again.

99a0238a72bb0f96.voiceContent: Good morning! The dew at dawn is perfect for brewing tea, so I made some for you. Drink up, and then we'll head off!

9e4b2c0b0e6e1b37.voiceContent: Every day's the same... Stir-Fried Shrimp, day in and day out. No matter how they prepare it, it always tastes the same. Ugh, ghastly! I really can't stand it anymore...

a55b0d0fba6d280c.voiceContent: Mmm! There's no better feeling than indulging in your favorite food... It's a shame that I can only afford to have a little bite.

a5d7fcff93255969.voiceContent: Per the tradition, actors must wrap their hair, put on full-face makeup and an elaborate costume, and make all sorts of other preparations before they take the stage. There's no doubt that an opera star in full attire looks spectacular, but achieving this look is frightfully exhausting. So I perform without hair and makeup whenever I have the option â€” and if I must perform in full dress, I try to select a costume that isn't too heavy. Fortunately, the good folks at Heyu Tea House are quite lenient with us. Otherwise, we'd be working ourselves to early graves.

a8ce71b646e05b67.voiceContent: *gasp* Dâ€”Did you hear that? Whew, it really startled me!

add12ffe0c682802.voiceContent: Ugh, the curtain's not down yet...

aee0b2b2ee249cb2.voiceContent: My waistband has been feeling a little snug these last couple of days... Methinks I perchance have overindulged...

b15299d942311a74.voiceContent: There's a chill in the air tonight, so you mustn't stay out late. Good night!

b4a653fb12598486.voiceContent: I have yet to see the Yuheng ever attend an opera performance. Now that I think about it, whenever I happen to see her out on the street, she always seems to be in a great hurry.

b5ec3f340a870c84.voiceContent: Huh? You like rock 'n' roll? Oh, that's great! I'll be sure to bring you along the next time I go out to see a show. And when I get back, I can just tell the senior troupe members that I went out to visit you... Hehe, that way, they won't have any reason to get on my case about going out.

cc4dc9c23e577154.voiceContent: One of my absolute favorite pastimes is trying out all kinds of new beverages. I've already tried all the sophisticated-sounding drinks that previous generations came up with â€” you know, like Pine Nectar Tea and Snow Blossom Tea. I'm beginning to worry that I'll run out of new drinks to try soon. You don't happen to have any recommendations, do you?

d28c29ea3626b849.voiceContent: We have some grand performances coming up soon, and it just so happens that we have an opening for someone to play the part of a skilled swordfighter. I think you'd be a perfect match for the part. How about it? Would you like to join our troupe? We can even enjoy some tea together in between acts.

d37ab76f16595cdc.voiceContent: Let's go listen to tonight's storytelling performance together. Liu Su's rendition of Ring of Raining Blades is most sublime!

dab8e467b4aafc8e.voiceContent: Ah yes, Hu Tao. Very expressive face, and she has a sharp mind too â€” you can be discussing the most mundane thing in the world, and she'll always bring out a string of witty remarks. I admire her a lot. There's never a dull moment when you have friends like her around.

dd584ad236ca26aa.voiceContent: No need to stand on ceremony. I'll just take this.

df9db562521b51a0.voiceContent: Hmm, which opera shall we perform today?

e0a690b9e4584395.voiceContent: Ahhh... Yes, I shall spare myself the hair and makeup routine today, and happily idle my time away!

e57668ab1c07eaec.voiceContent: The art of the spear is a vast and profound discipline... There is an almost infinite number of things one can learn. I am glad to have had you by my side during my training. Haha, I believe I've grasped the basics now. I daresay you'd better be careful when we're sparring together in the future.

e5daa30339a6ae65.voiceContent: In her youth, my mother was a famous opera singer in Liyue Harbor, and I learned all the operas I know from her. But, you could never imagine how strict she was with me as a teacher. Thinking back on it now, I... *sigh* No, no, no, I'd rather not think about it at all.

e67dc978610d0cb4.voiceContent: The customs of the opera are very particular, and are passed down from generation to generation. Sometimes I find that I only know the hows but not the whys behind what we do. But when speaking with Zhongli, it is abundantly evident that he knows the origins behind almost everything. Who wouldn't be delighted to have such a connoisseur in their audience?

e857d50098ec0755.voiceContent: Tianshu Meat, Black-Back Perch Stew, Cured Pork Dry Hotpot... Oh, I just want them all! Unfortunately, I basically never get to eat such things, but... um, if you don't mind me asking... Can you cook any of those dishes?

eab3a92a3df50456.voiceContent: What a sight to behold, the sun so warm and radiant...

f362f5386013a8e6.voiceContent: Oh, what a magnificent feast! Wait a second, I'll grab us some drinks to accompany the meal.

f9f42d7e2a03c8c2.voiceContent: My hobbies? Well, opera, of course! It's what I truly love and it's what I will be pursuing for the rest of my life.

fe8eeee22821b6ee.voiceContent: Oh, so you are also acquainted with Xingqiu? Haha, he is quite the clever one, and with a sharp wit as well. The moment you let your guard down, you're at risk of becoming the butt of one of his practical jokes... Don't say I didn't warn you.
